## Stripe Webhook Events to Handle

- `payment_intent.succeeded` - Booking payment captured
- `payment_intent.canceled` - Booking expired or cancelled
- `charge.refunded` - Refund processed
- `transfer.created` - Provider payout initiated
- `transfer.failed` - Provider payout failed (alert admin)
- `invoice.paid` - Guardian subscription payment processed
- `customer.subscription.updated` - Guardian subscription changed
- `customer.subscription.deleted` - Guardian subscription cancelled

All webhook handlers must be idempotent. Maintain a `processed_webhook_events` table to deduplicate.

